@startuml
title Node.js server.js 이벤트 루프 흐름
skinparam backgroundColor #F7F9FC
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #2B5876
  LifeLineBorderColor #2B5876
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EAF2FF
  ParticipantBorderColor #2B5876
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ParticipantFontColor #1F2D3D
  ActorBorderColor #2B5876
  ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ActorFontColor #1F2D3D
}

autonumber

actor "Client\n(Browser/curl)" as Client
participant "OS Network I/O" as OS
participant "Event Loop\n(libuv)" as Loop
participant "Main Thread\n(Call Stack)" as Main
participant "HTTP Server\n(node:http)" as Server

Main -> Server: createServer(handler)
Main -> Server: listen(3000, 127.0.0.1)
Server -> Loop: 소켓 감시 등록
Loop -> Main: listen 콜백 실행\nconsole.log(...)
Main --> Loop: Idle(대기)

loop 요청이 들어올 때마다
  Client -> OS: HTTP 요청
  OS -> Loop: 소켓 이벤트 전달
  Loop -> Main: handler(req, res) 실행
  Main -> Server: statusCode=200\nsetHeader("Content-Type","text/plain")
  Main -> Server: res.end("Hello World")
  Server -> OS: 응답 쓰기 위임(비동기 I/O)
  OS --> Client: HTTP 200 + Hello World
  Main --> Loop: 다음 이벤트 대기
end

note right of Main
동기 CPU 작업이 길면
이 구간이 막혀서
다른 요청도 지연됨
(이벤트 루프 블로킹)
end note
@enduml